### 获取所有学生
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

### 根据ID获取学生
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students/STU_001
Content-Type: application/json

### 根据专业代码获取学生
GET http://localhost:8080/api/students/major/CS
Content-Type: application/json

### 添加学生
POST http://localhost:8080/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentId": "STU_TEST",
  "name": "测试学生",
  "gender": "男",
  "birthDate": "2000-01-01",
  "phone": "13800138000",
  "majorCode": "MAJOR_TEST",
  "userId": "USER_TEST",
  "password": "password123",
  "status": 1
}

### 更新学生
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/students/STU_TEST
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "更新后的测试学生",
  "gender": "女",
  "birthDate": "2000-02-02",
  "phone": "13800138001",
  "majorCode": "MAJOR_TEST",
